# Learning Management System (LMS)

## Project Overview
This is a Learning Management System built with Java, JDBC, and MySQL.

## Setup Instructions
1. Clone the repository
2. Configure database properties in src/main/resources/config/database.properties
3. Run schema.sql to create database tables
4. Build the project using Maven: mvn clean install

## Features
- Student Management
- Course Management
- Assignment Handling
- User Authentication

## Technologies Used
- Java
- JDBC
- MySQL
- Maven
